strings: <voice_0x01000D11><se_low>King Trode: It never used to be this difficult to get a drink...

<voice_0x01000D12><se_low>King Trode: Another thing that wretched Dhoulmagus
is responsible for!
Confound him and confound this curse!

<voice_0x01000D13><se_low>King Trode: But it's Medea who's really suffering.
Turned into a horse just when she was
betrothed to be married...

<voice_0x01000D14><se_low>King Trode: Oh! You're back already!
That was unduly expedient of you.
So, have you found out where Dhoulmagus is?

<voice_0x01000D15><se_low>King Trode: What was that!?
I thought I heard Medea...
